<div class="scroll-posts" id="2017/04/03/forget-trump-tv-bernie-sanders-has-struck-gold-with-his-new-online-show/">
<section class="title-container">
<h1>Forget Trump TV. Bernie Sanders has struck gold with his new Facebook Live show</h1>
<h2>Bernie Sanders continues the message of his campaign by tackling real issues on his Facebook Live show</h2>

<section class="writer-container writer-app-wrapper">
<div class="writer_info_wrapper">
<h5><span>By </span>
<a href="/web/20201211024115/https://www.salon.com/writer/charlie-may">Charlie May</a>
</h5>
<h6>April 3, 2017 9:55PM (UTC)</h6>
</div>
